          "type": "code",
          "language": "python",
          "line_numbers": true,
          "style": "code",
          "source": "import numpy as np\n\ndef laplacian(u, L):\n    n = u.size\n    k = 2*np.pi*np.fft.fftfreq(n, d=L/n)\n    return np.real(np.fft.ifft(-(k**2) * np.fft.fft(u)))\n"
        },
